 faculties: <cit><quote>f. is smothered in surmise,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 140</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as her appetite shall play the god with his weak f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.354" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 354</bibl></cit>.
